    "Software engineers will require new skills, such as refining software that is generated automatically, feeding learning engines, and investigating behaviors that are not explicable.",
    "Generative AI will accelerate software development.",
    "However, be wary of marketing hype about quick fixes for developing secure and resilient software using non-deterministic technology.Many recommendations for agile project management are provided by GenAI, which can be especially helpful early on when knowledge and experience with agile methods are scarce.",
    "How much GenAI can help with tasks involving highly experienced people still needs to be clarified?",
    "Although simple prompt structures seem to work well for now, there is a fascinating field for further research into more intricate prompt designs and their combinations.Fig. 1.1Fig."
